As far as I can see you have not added your subcomponent to the main component. To add a subcomponent you need to specify it in `subcomponents` parameter of a module inside the main component. There is an example in [the documentation](https://dagger.dev/subcomponents.html#adding-a-subcomponent-to-a-parent-component)
